'''SRM Engineering College''',now the [[SRM Institute of Science and Technology]] was an Engineering College located some 50 km from [[Chennai]], [[South India]]. Previosly functioning under the [[Anna University]], the Institute gained the [[Deemed university|Deemed status]] in [[2003]]-[[2004|04]]. 

SRM Engineering College was started by Pachaimuthu in memoriam of his mother Smt.Valliammai. {{citation needed}}

